Make sure to replace `'your-opensearch-endpoint'`, `'your-index-name'`, `'field_name'`, and `'filter_value'` with your actual OpenSearch endpoint, index name, field name, and the value you want to filter on respectively. Additionally, you may need to install the `elasticsearch` package using pip (`pip install elasticsearch`) if you haven't already.

